{"tid":409282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"根本快樂不快樂都是奢侈的","createTime":"2017-09-22T02:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T03:13:08.000Z","uid":124427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83c49a3d2f5344bab0425f1e5aef478d1315328f","tid":409282,"uid":124427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"成日都有人講話快樂係一件奢侈嘅事<br />\n因為人生本身就係全滿煩惱同悲哀<br />\n如果能夠喺日常中開心就已經係一個bonus<br />\n然而追求快樂就好似追求一啲非必需品咁<br />\n<br />\n但日子一日一日咁過 每日過住行屍走肉嘅生活<br />\n慢慢 慢慢 就會對世事都麻木咗<br />\n就發現唔單止有得開心係bonus<br />\n根本唔開心都一個bonus 都係奢侈的"},{"pid":"5c313c7c519e76a9634088f9fc61fa5d27023fc2","tid":409282,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"人之初"},{"pid":"48e9471c5bb922eac611315011a2627cc72e03b1","tid":409282,"uid":124427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人之初</blockquote><br />\n就是無情感的"},{"pid":"981b263e297d41bb3026e5445b12a57b1574d2f4","tid":409282,"uid":124427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"有時候見啲人好努力地嘗試去開心<br />\n但到佢地得到快樂 或者終於無煩惱嘅時候<br />\n又會走去搵嘢去煩 又要搞到自己唔開心<br />\n但諗下 根本兩者都係不必要的"},{"pid":"988bcd4698d72429452b4c75a393d76f1fc9a2c7","tid":409282,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬啱啱升中學？"},{"pid":"e3ce65c04993de480adb0f23b315a8a48fab0ef7","tid":409282,"uid":124427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬啱啱升中學？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 想話完全唔知我噏乜對不對？<br />\n我本身未打完錯手post左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}